{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775859825644,"sessionID":"ses_286839261ffe5vMhuvJXyxZ1Bh","part":{"id":"prt_d797c751d001Tc3IZioVdlBwDj","messageID":"msg_d797c6e82001BkXPYo64I68e1q","sessionID":"ses_286839261ffe5vMhuvJXyxZ1Bh","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_1da250a4ac80488fabd6ce3b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore project structure","prompt":"Explore the project at /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z to understand:\n1. The overall project structure (list top-level directories and key files)\n2. Look for any existing tasks.md, spec.md, design.md, or similar planning documents\n3. Look for any existing metadata service or data model related code\n4. Check if there's a cmd/cli directory or similar Python CLI structure\n5. Look for any ST-3 stage completion artifacts or documentation\n6. Find examples of how tasks are structured in this project (if any exist)\n\nReturn a comprehensive summary of what you find, including file paths and relevant content snippets.","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_286837b3bffeivdSHGNUvWYjLL (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nHere is a comprehensive summary of the project exploration:\n\n---\n\n## 1. Overall Project Structure\n\n**Root:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z`\n\n### Top-Level Directories and Key Files\n\n| Entry | Description |\n|-------|-------------|\n| `cmd/cli/` | Python CLI package (Typer-based `kubectl-agentcube`) |\n| `pkg/` | Go server packages |\n| `agentd/` | Idle cleanup controller (Go) |\n| `client-go/` | Generated Kubernetes Go client for AgentRuntime CRDs |\n| `changes/` | 25 change requests (AR-001 through AR-025), each with proposal/design/spec/tasks |\n| `ci-cd/` | CI/CD design and spec |\n| `cli-toolkit/` | CLI toolkit design and spec |\n| `code-execution/` | Code execution module design and spec |\n| `deployment/` | Deployment design and spec |\n| `idle-cleanup/` | Idle cleanup design and spec |\n| `integrations/` | Integrations design and spec |\n| `python-sdk/` | Python SDK design and spec |\n| `sandbox-orchestration/` | Sandbox orchestration spec |\n| `session-routing/` | Session routing design and spec |\n| `session-store/` | Session store design and spec |\n| `testing/` | Testing manifest |\n| `go.mod`, `go.sum` | Go module files |\n| `coverage.out` | Go coverage output |\n| `design.md` | Root-level design doc (AR-020: CLI pack command) |\n| `delta-spec.md` | Root-level delta spec (AR-023: CLI invoke/status) |\n| `tasks.md` | Root-level tasks file (AR-023: CLI invoke/status) |\n| `project.md` | Project context for AgentCube |\n| `proposal.md` | AR-024: DockerService encapsulation proposal |\n| `.sdd_prompt.md` | SDD prompt containing full CLI architecture reference |\n\n### Project Purpose (from `project.md`)\n\n> AgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents. It provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through session-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\n\n**Tech Stack:** Go 1.24 (server), Python >=3.10 (CLI/SDK), Gin (Go HTTP), Typer (Python CLI), Kubernetes CRDs, Redis/Valkey, JWT RS256, Helm 3.\n\n---\n\n## 2. Planning Documents (tasks.md, spec.md, design.md, proposal.md)\n\nThe project follows a structured change request (AR = \"Agent Request\") workflow. Each AR in `changes/AR-XXX/` contains up to four documents:\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `proposal.md` | Purpose, scope, impact analysis, alternatives, acceptance criteria |\n| `design.md` | Full technical implementation details, data structures, API contracts, testing strategy |\n| `delta-spec.md` | Gherkin-style requirements (GIVEN/WHEN/THEN) for the specific change |\n| `tasks.md` | Actionable task breakdown with checkboxes, dependency graphs, parallelizable groups, acceptance criteria |\n\n**Root-level planning documents:**\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/tasks.md` -- AR-023 (CLI invoke/status tasks)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md` -- AR-020 (CLI pack command design)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md` -- AR-023 (CLI invoke/status delta spec)\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md` -- AR-024 (DockerService proposal)\n\nThere are 25 change requests (AR-001 through AR-025). The most recent is **AR-025: MetadataService and Data Models**, which is currently a skeleton (tasks are all \"TBD\").\n\n---\n\n## 3. Metadata Service and Data Model Code\n\n### MetadataService\n**File:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n\nContains:\n- **`AgentMetadata`** -- Pydantic `BaseModel` with 22 fields:\n  - Required: `agent_name`, `entrypoint`\n  - Validated enums: `language` (python/java), `build_mode` (local/cloud)\n  - Validated range: `port` (1-65535)\n  - Optional: `description`, `region`, `version`, `image`, `auth`, `agent_endpoint`, `workload_manager_url`, `router_url`, `readiness_probe_path`, `readiness_probe_port`, `agent_id`, `session_id`, `k8s_deployment`\n  - String defaults: `requirements_file=\"requirements.txt\"`, `registry_url=\"\"`, etc.\n\n- **`MetadataService`** -- Service class with methods:\n  - `load_metadata(workspace_path)` -- loads with fallback chain: `agent_metadata.yaml` -> `agent.yaml` -> `metadata.yaml`\n  - `save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)` -- writes to `agent_metadata.yaml`\n  - `update_metadata(workspace_path, updates)` -- load, merge, save, return\n  - `validate_workspace(workspace_path)` -- checks metadata file presence\n  - `_validate_python_workspace()` -- requires `*.py` files\n  - `_validate_java_workspace()` -- requires `pom.xml`\n\n### MetadataOptions\n**File:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/models/pack_models.py`\n\nA dataclass with 14 optional fields and a `from_options()` classmethod for CLI-to-model conversion.\n\n### Tests\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/tests/services/test_metadata_service.py`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/tests/services/test_metadata_model.py`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/tests/models/test_pack_models.py`\n\n---\n\n## 4. CLI Structure (cmd/cli)\n\n**Root:** `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/`\n\n### Package Layout\n\n```\ncmd/cli/\n├── pyproject.toml                     -- Dependencies, console script entry\n├── agentcube/\n│   ├── __init__.py                    -- __version__ = \"0.1.0\", exports\n│   ├── cli/\n│   │   ├── __init__.py\n│   │   └── main.py                    -- Typer app, all 6 commands\n│   ├── models/\n│   │   ├── __init__.py\n│   │   └── pack_models.py             -- MetadataOptions dataclass\n│   ├── runtime/\n│   │   ├── __init__.py                -- Re-exports runtimes + MetadataOptions\n│   │   ├── pack_runtime.py            -- PackRuntime\n│   │   ├── build_runtime.py           -- BuildRuntime\n│   │   ├── publish_runtime.py         -- PublishRuntime\n│   │   ├── invoke_runtime.py          -- InvokeRuntime\n│   │   └── status_runtime.py          -- StatusRuntime\n│   ├── services/\n│   │   ├── __init__.py\n│   │   ├── metadata_service.py        -- AgentMetadata + MetadataService\n│   │   ├── docker_service.py          -- DockerService\n│   │   ├── k8s_provider.py            -- KubernetesProvider\n│   │   └── agentcube_provider.py      -- AgentCubeProvider\n│   └── operations/\n│       └── __init__.py                -- Placeholder\n├── examples/\n│   ├── hello-agent/main.py\n│   └── math-agent/main.py\n└── tests/\n    ├── __init__.py\n    ├── cli/                           -- CLI command tests\n    ├── runtime/                       -- Runtime class tests\n    ├── services/                      -- Service tests\n    ├── models/                        -- Model tests\n    └── integration/                   -- E2E tests\n```\n\n### CLI Commands (from `main.py`)\n\n| Command | Description |\n|---------|-------------|\n| `pack` | Package an agent workspace |\n| `build` | Build a container image |\n| `publish` | Publish to Kubernetes (agentcube CR or k8s Deployment) |\n| `invoke` | Invoke a deployed agent with JSON payload |\n| `status` | Check status of a deployed agent |\n\nConsole script entry point: `kubectl-agentcube = \"agentcube.cli.main:app\"`\n\n---\n\n## 5. ST-3 Stage Completion Artifacts\n\nAll 25 AR tasks.md files reference ST-3 stage completion. There are two patterns:\n\n**Pattern 1 (older ARs, AR-002 through AR-012):**\n```\n> **Stage**: ST-3 (Design Complete)\n```\n\n**Pattern 2 (newer ARs, AR-013 through AR-025):**\n```\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n```\n\nThis indicates that **all change requests have completed the ST-3 (Design) stage** and are ready for implementation. The tasks.md files represent the implementation phase that follows design completion.\n\n---\n\n## 6. Task Structure Examples\n\nTasks follow a consistent template. Here is the structure from **AR-020 (CLI pack command)** -- the most detailed example with 20 tasks and 606 lines:\n\n### Task Template\n\n```markdown\n## T1. Task Title\n\n- [ ] 1.1 Specific sub-step\n- [ ] 1.2 Specific sub-step\n- [ ] 1.3 Specific sub-step with nested details\n- [ ] 1.4 Create corresponding test file\n\n**Verification:** `pytest path/to/test.py -v` all pass\n```\n\n### Key Structural Elements\n\n1. **Header metadata:**\n   ```\n   > **Module:** cmd/cli\n   > **Language:** Python\n   > **Size:** M\n   > **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n   > **Reference:** `changes/AR-XXX/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-XXX/design.md`, ...\n   > **Dependency:** AR-YYY -- description\n   ```\n\n2. **Tasks (T1, T2, ...):** Each task has numbered sub-steps with checkboxes (`- [ ]`) and a **Verification** line specifying the exact pytest command or validation step.\n\n3. **Task Dependencies section:** ASCII art dependency graph showing task ordering and parallelism opportunities.\n\n4. **Parallelizable Groups table:**\n   ```\n   | Group | Tasks | Prerequisites |\n   |-------|-------|---------------|\n   | G1 | T-1, T-7 | None |\n   ```\n\n5. **Acceptance Criteria table:**\n   ```\n   | # | Criterion | Command |\n   |---|-----------|---------|\n   | AC1 | pack command accepts all options | `kubectl-agentcube pack --help` |\n   ```\n\n### Two Task Granularity Levels Observed\n\n- **Coarse-grained** (e.g., AR-023, root `tasks.md`): ~15 tasks, each representing a class or major feature (T-1 through T-15)\n- **Fine-grained** (e.g., AR-020): ~20 tasks, each representing a single method or small unit of work (T1 through T20), with very detailed sub-steps\n\n### AR-025 Current State (Skeleton)\n\nThe most recent AR-025 (MetadataService and Data Models) tasks.md is a **skeleton** with placeholder content:\n```markdown\n## T1. TBD\n- [ ] TBD\n**Verification:** TBD\n```\n\nThis suggests AR-025 has been created with its proposal, design, and delta-spec documents fully written, but the tasks have not yet been broken down into actionable items.\n\n---\n\n## Summary of Key File Paths\n\n| Category | Path |\n|----------|------|\n| Root tasks.md | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/tasks.md` |\n| Root design.md | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/design.md` |\n| Root delta-spec.md | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md` |\n| CLI main entry | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py` |\n| MetadataService | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` |\n| MetadataOptions | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/models/pack_models.py` |\n| AR-025 proposal | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-025/proposal.md` |\n| AR-025 design | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-025/design.md` |\n| AR-025 delta-spec | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-025/delta-spec.md` |\n| AR-025 tasks | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-025/tasks.md` |\n| AR-020 tasks (best example) | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-020/tasks.md` |\n| SDD prompt (full CLI reference) | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/.sdd_prompt.md` |\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_286837b3bffeivdSHGNUvWYjLL","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore project structure","time":{"start":1775859696834,"end":1775859825641}}}}
